 <body>
  <h2 data-lake-id="\&quot;cJImQ\&quot;" id="\&quot;cJImQ\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua81ff675\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua81ff675\&quot;">高等数学</span></h2>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;Jm7j4\&quot;" id="\&quot;Jm7j4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue6cbe71b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue6cbe71b\&quot;">导数</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;JV8zi\&quot;" id="\&quot;JV8zi\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1e8d29a8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1e8d29a8\&quot;">导数的概念</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub53f9ffc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub53f9ffc\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub27e25bf\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub27e25bf\&quot;">导数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u747cefa0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u747cefa0\&quot;">（derivative）是微积分中的一个概念。函数在某一点的导数是指这个函数在这一点附近的变化率（即函数在这一点的切线斜率）。导数的本质是通过极限的概念对函数进行局部的线性逼近。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udec71024\&quot;" id="\&quot;udec71024\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719322590-549c90df-5862-41dd-86d1-3cefd7105b01.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua9449d04-e455-4a1e-bed9-65d153db620%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A364.8000183105469%2C%22height%22%3A238%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A380421%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A381%2C%22originHeight%22%3A249%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f1eeee%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u9a434d2f%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uabb9b982\&quot;" id="\&quot;uabb9b982\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u89ae2e13\&quot;" id="\&quot;u89ae2e13\&quot;">当函数的自变量在一点上产生一个增量</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa632a9407114c63854cd5ffe12d0be30.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Z9MEp%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u69b5bb5e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u69b5bb5e\&quot;">时，函数输出值的增量与自变量增量的比值在趋于0时的极限如果存在，即为在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F712ecf7894348e92d8779c3ee87eeeb0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Qu8cJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7af3c1c4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7af3c1c4\&quot;">处的导数，记作</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'(x)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F679bfb0b3a85dd0534f371cb5a1ebdf0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uWzxz%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5d993a88\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5d993a88\&quot;">、</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7Bdy%7D%7Bdx%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F65966b512f118fcc00b8c60ae86b2de1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pLT9y%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc954bd76\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc954bd76\&quot;">或</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22y'%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa94b066276ab7c671f6d0a673d4a93d2.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Cuj9u%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u146a5d2e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u146a5d2e\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u09a1a975\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09a1a975\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'(x)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clim_%7B%5C%5CDelta%20x%20%5C%5Cto%200%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bf(x%20%2B%20%5C%5CDelta%20x)%20-%20f(x)%7D%7B%5C%5CDelta%20x%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F5d5f3a1d4ccfbb78a502f2d70d849c5e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Pkzmm%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u69e71baf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u69e71baf\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uac9f265d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uac9f265d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2bf557cd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2bf557cd\&quot;">例如在运动学中，物体的位移对于时间的导数就是物体的瞬时速度：</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22v%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bds%7D%7Bdt%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ff558798c80f9ccd3a91386f5345ca7e6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TXUmT%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1394ce58\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1394ce58\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a322278\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a322278\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719336701-ce9027a0-bc9d-4d57-b4a5-c5c42e477d6f.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7f884bf0-8e36-4d07-91db-d609748bb33%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A343.8000183105469%2C%22height%22%3A241%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A407912%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A381%2C%22originHeight%22%3A267%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%E5%B7%A5AY%20AX%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A273%2C%22y%22%3A179%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B7%A5AY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A221%2C%22y%22%3A229%2C%22width%22%3A19%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22AX%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f5f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6e9a7292%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8115cec6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8115cec6\&quot;"><br /></p>
