  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;vWIXH\&quot;" id="\&quot;vWIXH\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufcd3c789\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufcd3c789\&quot;">利用导数求极值</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8de46297\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8de46297\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud1c4b716\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud1c4b716\&quot;">导数等于零的点称为函数的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5b08be28\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5b08be28\&quot;">驻点</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u891d0b3d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u891d0b3d\&quot;">（或极值可疑点），在这类点上函数可能会取得</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0dd9a5cd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0dd9a5cd\&quot;">极大值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubd70c9f6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubd70c9f6\&quot;">或</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u39d4e70f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u39d4e70f\&quot;">极小值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u08290c10\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08290c10\&quot;">。进一步判断则需要知道导数在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F48d05334b5b0710d63edb6b4b3ac631c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eue4k%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4f45bb87\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4f45bb87\&quot;">附近的符号。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua993a66c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua993a66c\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719384638-d951d871-a33e-4f52-adc0-56ce0cff61c6.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6ed7b866-eceb-4308-950f-3a8ed0af189%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A396.8000183105469%2C%22height%22%3A309%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A649007%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A456%2C%22originHeight%22%3A355%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22F(X)XSIN(X2)%20(2.8137.2.8081)%20F(X)SIN(X2)%2B2X2COS(X2)%20(1.3552%2C1.3076)%20(0.0)%20(2.1945%2C-2.1828)%202.5%201.5%200.0%203.0%201.0%202.0%200.5%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A191%2C%22y%22%3A1%2C%22width%22%3A92%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22F(X)XSIN(X2)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A300%2C%22y%22%3A25%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22(2.8137.2.8081)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A48%2C%22y%22%3A34%2C%22width%22%3A141%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%22F(X)SIN(X2)%2B2X2COS(X2)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A174%2C%22y%22%3A98%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22(1.3552%2C1.3076)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A48%2C%22y%22%3A177%2C%22width%22%3A27%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22(0.0)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A338%2C%22y%22%3A305%2C%22width%22%3A101%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22(2.1945%2C-2.1828)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A352%2C%22y%22%3A336%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%222.5%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A227%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A19%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%221.5%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A38%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%220.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A415%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%223.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A164%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%221.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A289%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%222.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A102%2C%22y%22%3A337%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%220.5%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f6f6%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u58fd3a42%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u547b5a11\&quot;" id="\&quot;u547b5a11\&quot;"><br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3a94fffb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3a94fffb\&quot;">例如，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x)%20%3D%20x%5E3%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F95b1f6253aaa788e97b7e020e56c5297.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YtveW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2f68dd80\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2f68dd80\&quot;">在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Febd911789dd2aa7f909ebdc723462975.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PswBx%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u51f83a0a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u51f83a0a\&quot;">处导数为0，但并不会取得极大值或者极小值。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua36f7245\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua36f7245\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719386830-63c26772-8a19-4a4d-9866-7883302b6663.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u1323bada-7648-4d9d-8bcf-dbd505880d6%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A261%2C%22height%22%3A431%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A320405%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A220%2C%22originHeight%22%3A363%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22Y%20X%20%201000%20750%20%E9%A9%BB%E7%82%B9%20(%E9%9D%9E%E6%9E%81%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9)%20250%20500%20-750%20-1000%2010%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A106%2C%22y%22%3A14%2C%22width%22%3A36%2C%22height%22%3A11%2C%22text%22%3A%22Y%20X%20%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A23%2C%22y%22%3A35%2C%22width%22%3A19%2C%22height%22%3A9%2C%22text%22%3A%221000%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A27%2C%22y%22%3A69%2C%22width%22%3A15%2C%22height%22%3A9%2C%22text%22%3A%22750%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A116%2C%22width%22%3A28%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E9%A9%BB%E7%82%B9%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A84%2C%22y%22%3A130%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22(%E9%9D%9E%E6%9E%81%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A27%2C%22y%22%3A139%2C%22width%22%3A15%2C%22height%22%3A8%2C%22text%22%3A%22250%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A25%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A17%2C%22height%22%3A7%2C%22text%22%3A%22500%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A22%2C%22y%22%3A276%2C%22width%22%3A20%2C%22height%22%3A8%2C%22text%22%3A%22-750%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A20%2C%22y%22%3A310%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A8%2C%22text%22%3A%22-1000%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A191%2C%22y%22%3A330%2C%22width%22%3A10%2C%22height%22%3A9%2C%22text%22%3A%2210%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22JtGsm%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua98996e1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua98996e1\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;uEWH7\&quot;" id="\&quot;uEWH7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud3e7d974\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud3e7d974\&quot;">二阶导数</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;szqau\&quot;" id="\&quot;szqau\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u48770bb9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48770bb9\&quot;">二阶导数的概念</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0bc90c55\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0bc90c55\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf5a09caf\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf5a09caf\&quot;">在微积分中，函数的二阶导数是函数导数的导数。粗略来说，某个量的二阶导数描述该量变化率变化的快慢。例如物体位置对时间的二阶导数是物体的瞬时加速度，即该物体速度随时间的变化率：</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bd%5E2s%7D%7Bdt%5E2%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F78cdbb2524aed4bc3b4dbb453441eb70.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xEKpN%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u49cc831c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u49cc831c\&quot;">。<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u12d841b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u12d841b8\&quot;">函数的二阶导数通常记作</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f''(x)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F3c936d3013b39fc56c7c150dc25a5822.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22z7Wge%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u804c675a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u804c675a\&quot;">、</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7Bd%5E2y%7D%7Bdx%5E2%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fefe2d5a1c4fca381a67a1dae4a2d3d19.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zbztn%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u07cdb770\&quot;" id="\&quot;u07cdb770\&quot;">或</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22y''%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F02b05883fcc6800c9ccca61fe632a81f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tzVqP%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucb6fa851\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucb6fa851\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc2f92fc0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc2f92fc0\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;YnBa2\&quot;" id="\&quot;YnBa2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u533287a2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u533287a2\&quot;">二阶导数与函数凹凸的关系</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6cfd86d7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6cfd86d7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf617d3a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf617d3a4\&quot;">函数的二阶导数描述了函数图像的凹凸方向和程度。若二阶导数在某区间恒为正，则函数在该区间向上弯（也称</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5616d96c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5616d96c\&quot;">下凸函数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8a67ef77\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8a67ef77\&quot;">）。反之，若二阶导数在某区间恒为负，则函数在该区间向下弯（也称</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0cdcafb7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0cdcafb7\&quot;">上凸函数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u80d7c355\&quot;" id="\&quot;u80d7c355\&quot;">）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u19eed4bb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19eed4bb\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719417190-1cdcf499-b792-4ab5-9b0b-f7eac94d8bf8.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u25b16649-12da-43ad-9a24-eddb9e395be%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A554.4%2C%22height%22%3A244%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A847215%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A693%2C%22originHeight%22%3A305%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22YF(X)%20Y%20F(X)%200%20X%20X1%20X%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A150%2C%22y%22%3A44%2C%22width%22%3A67%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22YF(X)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A491%2C%22y%22%3A48%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22Y%20F(X)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A385%2C%22y%22%3A236%2C%22width%22%3A17%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A631%2C%22y%22%3A241%2C%22width%22%3A13%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22X%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A477%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A16%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22X1%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A287%2C%22y%22%3A243%2C%22width%22%3A12%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%22X%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfcfc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u93d0f076%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udf777f65\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf777f65\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u88f1032c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u88f1032c\&quot;">若函数的二阶导数在某点左右异号，则图像由向上弯转为向下弯，或反之。这种点称之为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u33bba5a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u33bba5a4\&quot;">拐点</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2a9ed072\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2a9ed072\&quot;">。若二阶导数连续，则在该点处二阶导数为0。但反之二阶导数为0的点不一定是拐点。如</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x)%20%3D%20x%5E4%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fecb458611a9a0d9ff7cee827957105e2.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22B6vuP%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u58df81f7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u58df81f7\&quot;">，在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Febd911789dd2aa7f909ebdc723462975.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22mnG7a%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud1aca6a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud1aca6a4\&quot;">处有</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f''(0)%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ffc41022dc4012546bae0f0c174224056.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22N7DuH%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u78e1f584\&quot;" id="\&quot;u78e1f584\&quot;">，但在实数系上无拐点。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf93e294f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf93e294f\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719853637-51971bb1-ad62-47da-a840-6f998a3a2c96.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua1c09141-1c62-41f3-abc9-003dc5c7902%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A436.8%2C%22height%22%3A254%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A696032%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A546%2C%22originHeight%22%3A318%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9%20%E6%8B%90%E7%82%B9%20%E6%9E%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9%20X*%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A240%2C%22y%22%3A21%2C%22width%22%3A71%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A254%2C%22y%22%3A100%2C%22width%22%3A36%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E6%8B%90%E7%82%B9%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A345%2C%22y%22%3A213%2C%22width%22%3A71%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9E%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%80%BC%E7%82%B9%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A516%2C%22y%22%3A269%2C%22width%22%3A14%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22X*%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfafa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ub7061506%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1502c984\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1502c984\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf0c1b5a7\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf0c1b5a7\&quot;">二阶导数与凹凸性的关系有助于判断函数的驻点是否为极大值点或极小值点：<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u296212c1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u296212c1\&quot;">若</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'(x_0)%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf68d1da4a2be4f66dcd535dfc06df6e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LaLpQ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc2561349\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc2561349\&quot;">，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f''(x_0)%20%3C%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F706eb453ad02b0e533cf56f475af97d6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HpFHO%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udbb3c1a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;udbb3c1a1\&quot;">，则在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F48d05334b5b0710d63edb6b4b3ac631c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22m23if%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u70bb1d0e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u70bb1d0e\&quot;">取得极大值。<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaad5e51d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaad5e51d\&quot;">若</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'(x_0)%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf68d1da4a2be4f66dcd535dfc06df6e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AVjYk%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2a1f6cbf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2a1f6cbf\&quot;">，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f''(x_0)%20%3E%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fcff0f0785a8ea725c3b48e4be8ca1bed.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ztGEV%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua31497cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua31497cc\&quot;">，则在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F48d05334b5b0710d63edb6b4b3ac631c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22yyOuy%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue49690dc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue49690dc\&quot;">取得极小值。<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b483abb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b483abb\&quot;">若</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'(x_0)%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf68d1da4a2be4f66dcd535dfc06df6e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YPqLF%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2d9c4bb8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2d9c4bb8\&quot;">，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f''(x_0)%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F5d1a396d8b6e1e733ecca03206d73ca0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qmYmY%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf788568c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf788568c\&quot;">，则该点可能是拐点，也可能是极大值点或极小值点。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u71481c6c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u71481c6c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8df675c5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8df675c5\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;EEMVQ\&quot;" id="\&quot;EEMVQ\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf4e2669a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf4e2669a\&quot;">偏导与梯度</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;OLeg4\&quot;" id="\&quot;OLeg4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc86d11c6\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc86d11c6\&quot;">偏导数</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u116425ad\&quot;" id="\&quot;u116425ad\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udea2e08d\&quot;" id="\&quot;udea2e08d\&quot;">如果函数的自变量并非单个元素，而是多个元素，例如：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8da9b2ab\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8da9b2ab\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x%2C%20y)%20%3D%20x%5E2%20%2B%20xy%20%2B%20y%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F16a992c93d04786d9afa27b8ac34d97b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qJWNx%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u50dc52a9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u50dc52a9\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766719890318-b8162abc-c4fb-41f1-a29f-d0469b93a06f.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u1c203756-a019-4172-93cc-d8297576b45%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A361.6%2C%22height%22%3A317%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A717597%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A452%2C%22originHeight%22%3A396%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%2260%20F(X%2CY)%2040%2020%200%204%202%200%20%E4%B8%804%20-2%20-2%200%20-4%20X%204%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A389%2C%22y%22%3A101%2C%22width%22%3A22%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%2260%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A423%2C%22y%22%3A116%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A55%2C%22text%22%3A%22F(X%2CY)%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A386%2C%22y%22%3A143%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%2240%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A384%2C%22y%22%3A185%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%2220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A385%2C%22y%22%3A224%2C%22width%22%3A16%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A358%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A16%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%224%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A334%2C%22y%22%3A292%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%222%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A318%2C%22y%22%3A310%2C%22width%22%3A17%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A22%2C%22y%22%3A319%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%804%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A63%2C%22y%22%3A331%2C%22width%22%3A26%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22-2%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A293%2C%22y%22%3A336%2C%22width%22%3A25%2C%22height%22%3A17%2C%22text%22%3A%22-2%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A104%2C%22y%22%3A345%2C%22width%22%3A17%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%220%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A272%2C%22y%22%3A361%2C%22width%22%3A25%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%22-4%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A88%2C%22y%22%3A370%2C%22width%22%3A18%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22X%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A184%2C%22y%22%3A372%2C%22width%22%3A17%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%224%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f2f2f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uc22f8977%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucbf94227\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucbf94227\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u23288034\&quot;" id="\&quot;u23288034\&quot;">可将其中一个元素看作常数，此时可看作关于另一元素的函数。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7c007ceb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7c007ceb\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u945416d1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u945416d1\&quot;">例如，将</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F712ecf7894348e92d8779c3ee87eeeb0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22EUDlh%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u47d4a18b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u47d4a18b\&quot;">看作常数，此时</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F18f3c2855f0e85a1ac2257f64d917144.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22yDPEr%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua0812097\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua0812097\&quot;">可看作关于</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22y%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbf98c0ddcbe9c1e535f767c78c3aa813.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22IqXUV%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u41817726\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41817726\&quot;">的函数：</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f_x(y)%20%3D%20x%5E2%20%2B%20xy%20%2B%20y%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1b3952e4c8ce4bf4464ffdb957e6a87f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QHyFp%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6f8cb399\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6f8cb399\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u34a5868b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u34a5868b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7d67c4d6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7d67c4d6\&quot;">在</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%20%3D%20a%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2976b02f23eed3578b26537b5cdfcafa.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hywx5%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c42f731\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c42f731\&quot;">固定的情况下，可计算</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f_x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F25d24f7090d3bfd6dfd727894803b3cd.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Azz8h%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u34547209\&quot;" id="\&quot;u34547209\&quot;">关于</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22y%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbf98c0ddcbe9c1e535f767c78c3aa813.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fa25W%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udace72be\&quot;" id="\&quot;udace72be\&quot;">的导数：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc7ff2060\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc7ff2060\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f'_%7Bx%3Da%7D(y)%20%3D%20a%20%2B%202y%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd2c528cefdd655bfd13514185f19841e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UAgx0%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u85b3f9f7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u85b3f9f7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud49ae558\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud49ae558\&quot;">这种导数称为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u47f5fb36\&quot;" id="\&quot;u47f5fb36\&quot;">偏导数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u60985f72\&quot;" id="\&quot;u60985f72\&quot;">，一般记作：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u62aeedf4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u62aeedf4\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20y%7D(x%2C%20y)%20%3D%20x%20%2B%202y%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F665ef756b6939b321b257cf99765e815.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sDmsf%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uff90cfd1\&quot;" id="\&quot;uff90cfd1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue88b8277\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue88b8277\&quot;">更一般地来说，一个多元函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20x_n)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbaadbc61251602bdf6189471283487e4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rYnTt%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u11a0f578\&quot;" id="\&quot;u11a0f578\&quot;">在点</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22(a_1%2C%20a_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_n)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F01e4a8b43e7cfcef1ea7dc2f4a21434c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fECs0%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9eaaf458\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9eaaf458\&quot;">处对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_i%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F5b13ed0ae41bee9defcf75f2efc5f060.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OPFfH%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0cfa550\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0cfa550\&quot;">的偏导数定义为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ufe3adb55\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufe3adb55\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_i%7D(a_1%2C%20a_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_n)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clim_%7B%5C%5CDelta%20x_i%20%5C%5Cto%200%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bf(a_1%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_i%20%2B%20%5C%5CDelta%20x_i%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_n)%20-%20f(a_1%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_i%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_n)%7D%7B%5C%5CDelta%20x_i%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F036f18ac65dc22eb58eb997799d4dc77.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22yhX6D%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u79c7c0f5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u79c7c0f5\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;mBE2J\&quot;" id="\&quot;mBE2J\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua0693b04\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua0693b04\&quot;">方向导数</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u58cf639f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u58cf639f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1584f794\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1584f794\&quot;">偏导数可以看作是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uefc24620\&quot;" id="\&quot;uefc24620\&quot;">多元函数沿某个自变量轴方向的变化率</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u85d67227\&quot;" id="\&quot;u85d67227\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c3ab1ca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c3ab1ca\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u93b6f91a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u93b6f91a\&quot;">如果我们任意选取一个方向</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22l%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F6945e109777fe3fd777e8254f0ec0f0c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22JBPLe%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud348386c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud348386c\&quot;">，那么在某个点</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22(x_0%2C%20y_0)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F722e68ed71eb4284ecd12ffaa8d8d860.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wKXMB%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf67f5085\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf67f5085\&quot;">处，二元函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x%2C%20y)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2d17f54667d945961044c4c076f07a57.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LvWq1%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u02e72594\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02e72594\&quot;">沿着这个方向的变化率可以用极限定义为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf8e6b858\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf8e6b858\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20l%7D(x_0%2C%20y_0)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clim_%7B%5C%5CDelta%20l%20%5C%5Cto%200%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bf(x_0%20%2B%20%5C%5CDelta%20x%2C%20y_0%20%2B%20%5C%5CDelta%20y)%20-%20f(x_0%2C%20y_0)%7D%7B%5C%5CDelta%20l%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F090df89b6364c3e65e7438a737f144f2.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22SIIAr%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u00f1ec4a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u00f1ec4a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1a65110e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1a65110e\&quot;">这里，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20l%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4aaf1416c50da8e9a4805c271df1f0f3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pGdgJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b2ba10f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b2ba10f\&quot;">就是沿方向</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22l%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F6945e109777fe3fd777e8254f0ec0f0c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22L2P2z%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uadf29623\&quot;" id="\&quot;uadf29623\&quot;">的微小改变量，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa632a9407114c63854cd5ffe12d0be30.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eIunV%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue6787894\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue6787894\&quot;">和</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20y%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F70f4cd5f7966b1e991dcdd8efe5d2986.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22NiE3F%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud2e32873\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud2e32873\&quot;">与</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20l%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4aaf1416c50da8e9a4805c271df1f0f3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Q2Fg1%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9d5d02b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9d5d02b8\&quot;">的关系为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1b09a8a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1b09a8a1\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5CDelta%20x%20%3D%20%5C%5CDelta%20l%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Ccos%20%5C%5Calpha%2C%20%5C%5Cquad%20%5C%5CDelta%20y%20%3D%20%5C%5CDelta%20l%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Ccos%20%5C%5Cbeta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0c4899f99376a2ab672a3aa3cd9dd421.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Bl4m0%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub541465b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub541465b\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
