   <li fid="\&quot;uc42a0990\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u62e9a263\&quot;" id="\&quot;u62e9a263\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u653f2062\&quot;" id="\&quot;u653f2062\&quot;">向量与标量相乘：标量与向量每个元素相乘</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub123d4e0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub123d4e0\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22c%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%3D%20%5Bcx_1%2C%20cx_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20cx_n%5D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F55acca2782edb77b1513bd5be979f8c8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YpKro%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u29ec7f89\&quot;" start="\&quot;4\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ua652b98e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub696315e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub696315e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5454c9b2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5454c9b2\&quot;">向量内积：又称向量点乘，两向量对应元素乘积之和，结果为标量</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue2bab8a8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue2bab8a8\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7By%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20x_i%20y_i%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa0487db861fb2ad809d358da36588491.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gYtno%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;ua1866742\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u2b34c3f4\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ue1c25fb4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue1c25fb4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4831637\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4831637\&quot;">两向量之间夹角表示为</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2e077ffc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2e077ffc\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ccos%20%5C%5Ctheta%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7By%7D%7D%7B%7C%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%7C%7C%5C%5Cmathbf%7By%7D%7C%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf558743488249ff70f250f349250042.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22blrQM%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
