  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;lu4TB\&quot;" id="\&quot;lu4TB\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7cb9c0dc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7cb9c0dc\&quot;">向量范数</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3b95a2e3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3b95a2e3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u08ff1e2a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08ff1e2a\&quot;">范数（norm）是具有“长度”概念的函数。</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u5ff6741d\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ucee97ee4\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e166124\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e166124\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1029744a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1029744a\&quot;">L0范数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaf67ad85\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaf67ad85\&quot;">（也称0范数）</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u18a35ca0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u18a35ca0\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5C%7C%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%5C%5C%7C_0%20%3D%20%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%9D%9E%E9%9B%B6%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Feed92d9346c74027c8e4f39e851fa8db.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22iKxSX%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u1695f563\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u9c7b8003\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;udc4c2213\&quot;" id="\&quot;udc4c2213\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u19cd21af\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19cd21af\&quot;">例如：</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%3D%20%5B2%2C%200%2C%205%2C%200%2C%208%5D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fad5b7d789d6a9bdf764b6e8275dda2b3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OxgtJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue5b2d7ad\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue5b2d7ad\&quot;">，则</span>
