  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;uu6re\&quot;" id="\&quot;uu6re\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u850ef0c8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u850ef0c8\&quot;">矩阵与张量</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;UWebw\&quot;" id="\&quot;UWebw\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u24c64739\&quot;" id="\&quot;u24c64739\&quot;">矩阵的概念</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uea4d1046\&quot;" id="\&quot;uea4d1046\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4bec39c7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4bec39c7\&quot;">一个</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22m%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0d03506bd44db15467257d19f46f1fc1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22bz9T7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc7dd8a46\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc7dd8a46\&quot;">的矩阵（matrix）是一个有m行n列元素的矩形阵列。用</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fcfdf131e0520efb20a6d1062b8b34a55.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22bdyrJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0b6d5fc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0b6d5fc\&quot;">表示所有实数矩阵的向量空间。</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u32ea3fbd\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;uc71fff41\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u18f10be8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u18f10be8\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucc4c1488\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucc4c1488\&quot;">方阵</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6723068\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6723068\&quot;">：行数等于列数的矩阵</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua93532e0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua93532e0\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20a_%7B11%7D%20%26%20a_%7B12%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7B1n%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20a_%7B21%7D%20%26%20a_%7B22%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7B2n%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20a_%7Bn1%7D%20%26%20a_%7Bn2%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7Bnn%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F8bea1b447897190398071201ae6bbd2c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OwbBU%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u2d007ba1\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ue7897f6c\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf44026c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf44026c2\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u827478cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u827478cc\&quot;">对角矩阵</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4d1043a3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4d1043a3\&quot;">：主对角线以外元素全为0的方阵</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1d218242\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1d218242\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctext%7Bdiag%7D(d_1%2C%20d_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20d_n)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20d_1%20%26%200%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%200%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%26%20d_2%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%200%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%26%200%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20d_n%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Feea921eec0f7770ace0d849098b1ae3a.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HLh5r%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u4740b280\&quot;" start="\&quot;3\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ufc45b121\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5415dc21\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5415dc21\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc65c6c22\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc65c6c22\&quot;">单位矩阵</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f7bd6a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f7bd6a4\&quot;">：主对角线元素全为1的对角矩阵</span></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u10e73ab2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u10e73ab2\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22I%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%201%20%26%200%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%200%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%26%201%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%200%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%26%200%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%201%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1577af23e62b2c3ce53f4ea1fd3d7097.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nmOgC%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u76645517\&quot;" id="\&quot;u76645517\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;Bn3A0\&quot;" id="\&quot;Bn3A0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud3cf7a7f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud3cf7a7f\&quot;">矩阵乘法</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaa0eff73\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaa0eff73\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5f736fae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5f736fae\&quot;">矩阵乘法运算</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua46cc8c5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua46cc8c5\&quot;"><br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u636191a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u636191a1\&quot;">两个矩阵的乘法仅当矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TDTPa%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucbfe6826\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucbfe6826\&quot;">的列数和矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TrH1l%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud97b487c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud97b487c\&quot;">的行数相等时才能定义。如</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa29eb9ee2111d8b446d60a4ff740a5dc.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Cc1dw%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf8b434b2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf8b434b2\&quot;">，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bn%20%5C%5Ctimes%20p%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4e5ab2e79c358c31eadd032f2a6a0a57.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ziuKB%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f3144fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f3144fd\&quot;">，它们的乘积</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22C%20%3D%20AB%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20p%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2875f1713b572ddf5c0966c08410c163.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nAloS%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucb25ed2e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucb25ed2e\&quot;">，其中：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1f1c1881\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1f1c1881\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22c_%7Bij%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bk%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20a_%7Bik%7D%20b_%7Bkj%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ff7dab8812f1b91c782d37d77b13e75b8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ss6x6%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u522a808c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u522a808c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uebbbbd0a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uebbbbd0a\&quot;">例如：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u79bbfeac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u79bbfeac\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
