  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;uGUgQ\&quot;" id="\&quot;uGUgQ\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf5ce540\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf5ce540\&quot;">矩阵的逆</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf32cc5b2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf32cc5b2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf656f04a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf656f04a\&quot;">对于方阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tqimG%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3e29c2bf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3e29c2bf\&quot;">，如果存在另一个方阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%5E%7B-1%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7dc6d0c9a5a080ea5420c072061b9d9b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vv1CZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc17ffd88\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc17ffd88\&quot;">，使得</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22AA%5E%7B-1%7D%20%3D%20I%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc2db5d788e7a50f8b48764928b1dc5d9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YeZ9t%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0214b81\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0214b81\&quot;">成立，此时</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%5E%7B-1%7DA%20%3D%20I%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7cee03ac2ab17b59c8fe532fb9719d18.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YILW3%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2b3b3612\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2b3b3612\&quot;">也同样成立。称</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%5E%7B-1%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7dc6d0c9a5a080ea5420c072061b9d9b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22NST4I%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2917d107\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2917d107\&quot;">为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dUx0V%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6855b19c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6855b19c\&quot;">的逆矩阵。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7504792c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7504792c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u11afab47\&quot;" id="\&quot;u11afab47\&quot;">例如：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uec8604b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;uec8604b9\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%201%20%26%202%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%203%20%26%205%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cquad%20A%5E%7B-1%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20-5%20%26%202%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%203%20%26%20-1%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F524065af52c2cb14ae6bc72f80395676.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eQtv1%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
