  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6c76a1e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6c76a1e9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u67489d14\&quot;" id="\&quot;u67489d14\&quot;">矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa29eb9ee2111d8b446d60a4ff740a5dc.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Mlmhr%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub39cca58\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub39cca58\&quot;">的向量化</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctext%7Bvec%7D(A)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd4519912b5afca491fc4aa5dc496a5a3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nZI6Q%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7407e491\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7407e491\&quot;">将矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22kmEVL%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc6f2f88c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc6f2f88c\&quot;">的元素按列排列成一个</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22mn%20%5C%5Ctimes%201%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F915caab03b959fbd13e2b712894d7d78.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DMwEQ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u75a33b48\&quot;" id="\&quot;u75a33b48\&quot;">的向量。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua938eb0c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua938eb0c\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctext%7Bvec%7D(A)%20%3D%20%5Ba_%7B11%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7Bm1%7D%2C%20a_%7B12%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7Bm2%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7B1n%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7Bmn%7D%5D%5ET%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2df05f6f766ea2a7ac720d87ed038c99.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22BetG7%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf4438fc0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf4438fc0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufcdf03ca\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufcdf03ca\&quot;">矩阵也可以转化为行向量，称为矩阵的行向量化</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctext%7Brvec%7D(A)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4ddf25626b79dc1853be27e7950b6b13.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lGtif%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u32617f0d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32617f0d\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u03101da0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u03101da0\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctext%7Brvec%7D(A)%20%3D%20%5Ba_%7B11%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7B1n%7D%2C%20a_%7B21%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7B2n%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7Bm1%7D%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20a_%7Bmn%7D%5D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F5e7b573a3055eb5f4e5d353289e2d7ff.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gOmqg%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2eee5d9\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2eee5d9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud4d8aeeb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud4d8aeeb\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc5bf0133\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc5bf0133\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6fc97e89\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6fc97e89\&quot;">例如：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf1f67adf\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf1f67adf\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%201%20%26%202%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%203%20%26%204%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7b500704d499a07bf7f014ed19015654.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MRbqI%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ul list="\&quot;u04909b97\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u3f15a12e\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7b59001c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7b59001c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u02d47649\&quot;" id="\&quot;u02d47649\&quot;">列向量化：</span></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaee07884\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaee07884\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
