   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F44bafa0005cfea4d38a6350d07a8994d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nBcSn%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5dcb654c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5dcb654c\&quot;">的内积记作</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22(A%2C%20B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F07fd6080a04be75e237d8c1634904d0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KluVB%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u51191a9b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u51191a9b\&quot;">，它是两个矩阵对应元素乘积之和，是一个标量。</span></p>
