   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22m%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0d03506bd44db15467257d19f46f1fc1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tYNpW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub42f8d0b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub42f8d0b\&quot;">的矩阵。</span></p>
