  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d925aa4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d925aa4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue2430c13\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue2430c13\&quot;">矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bm%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa29eb9ee2111d8b446d60a4ff740a5dc.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wSbFV%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u20aa30f9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u20aa30f9\&quot;">和矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bp%20%5C%5Ctimes%20q%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F56d846d1f00de27a7fdc2b04254e0020.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22JSaVz%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8fc7aeb5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8fc7aeb5\&quot;">的Kronecker积记作</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Cotimes%20B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F06753b0556b989cd4d7154ff0ffab783.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pY5Ya%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc57210fa\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc57210fa\&quot;">，它是矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GluNO%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6048901f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6048901f\&quot;">中每个元素与矩阵</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22I8diY%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9d08fb6\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9d08fb6\&quot;">的乘积，是一个</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22mp%20%5C%5Ctimes%20nq%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb9c46e9902ccfe18b04c785dd3422f06.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22phSQd%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufa6d9e96\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufa6d9e96\&quot;">的矩阵。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u064d1ee9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u064d1ee9\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22(A%20%5C%5Cotimes%20B)_%7Bij%7D%20%3D%20%5Ba_%7Bij%7D%20B%5D_%7Bi%3D1%2Cj%3D1%7D%5E%7Bm%2Cn%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F3f8bbcb444a81ba93e3d4c513d04c5a9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wFUie%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7b215a6a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7b215a6a\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Cotimes%20B%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20a_%7B11%7DB%20%26%20a_%7B12%7DB%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7B1n%7DB%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20a_%7B21%7DB%20%26%20a_%7B22%7DB%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7B2n%7DB%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20a_%7Bm1%7DB%20%26%20a_%7Bm2%7DB%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20a_%7Bmn%7DB%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4f24fa7ef72281a8b2757688ee9d435f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22E3IMT%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub9622580\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub9622580\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uec7a2461\&quot;" id="\&quot;uec7a2461\&quot;">Kronecker积也称为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9b140910\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9b140910\&quot;">直积或张量积。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud31ef641\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud31ef641\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u108bbb5d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u108bbb5d\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;d2ZXD\&quot;" id="\&quot;d2ZXD\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u61a503ed\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61a503ed\&quot;">张量</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1e5376a6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1e5376a6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc470b02d\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc470b02d\&quot;">张量（tensor）可视为多维数组，是标量，1维向量和2维矩阵的n维推广。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udf4d73e1\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf4d73e1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4ae1a09f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4ae1a09f\&quot;">例如：3维张量</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u19bd1c88\&quot;" id="\&quot;u19bd1c88\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathcal%7BT%7D%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5E%7Bd_1%20%5C%5Ctimes%20d_2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20d_3%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F49b00141710e9bf67e47d724adc84ce7.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fgVak%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u887f472c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u887f472c\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;LIIS4\&quot;" id="\&quot;LIIS4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0344ad18\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0344ad18\&quot;">矩阵求导</span></h3>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uafc84ca4\&quot;" id="\&quot;uafc84ca4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf7bf8d80\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf7bf8d80\&quot;">矩阵求导的本质是：函数对变元的每个元素分别求导后，将结果按向量/矩阵的结构重新组织呈现（而非简单的&quot;数值导数&quot;，而是保留向量/矩阵的维度形式）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u25e8b869\&quot;" id="\&quot;u25e8b869\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0fc87a68\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0fc87a68\&quot;">为精准理解，先对「变元（自变量）」和「函数」做统一的符号与定义规范：</span></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u902e2611\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u0a02843a\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf0f6794a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf0f6794a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8ca8ce3c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8ca8ce3c\&quot;">变元的符号规则</span></li>
  </ol>
  <ul list="\&quot;u8be3f908\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u095c2c46\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u921c0050\&quot;" id="\&quot;u921c0050\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufb932c7c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufb932c7c\&quot;">实向量变元</span></strong></li>
  </ul>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u36ca7066\&quot;" id="\&quot;u36ca7066\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"=""><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u05675284\&quot;" id="\&quot;u05675284\&quot;">设 </span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%3D%20%5Bx_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cdots%2C%20x_m%5D%5ET%20%5C%5Cin%20%5C%5Cmathbb%7BR%7D%5Em%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbe21c9d615cb01d57871e7afffb218e5.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zoaap%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub08af36c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub08af36c\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3bf2a48e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3bf2a48e\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-indent:" 2em\"=""><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3beca734\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3beca734\&quot;">解释：</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5Bx_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cdots%2C%20x_m%5D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F30d1d7d7c53c1906026856e3ebe47923.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22IvAPs%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u449d3498\&quot;" id="\&quot;u449d3498\&quot;"> 是行形式的元素列表，上标 </span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22T%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1553dae3cc5c15cddb4f5b5a367b0aba.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22iSJsv%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u77971df3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77971df3\&quot;"> 表示转置，转置后将行向量转化为 </span>
