       <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7BX%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7fd2ecce63e6b52b6164d90bcce651fe.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uOfrK%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p></td>
     <td data-lake-id="\&quot;u6ae74841\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6ae74841\&quot;"><p data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f121707\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f121707\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" left\"=""><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufb5df025\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufb5df025\&quot;">输入是 </span>
       <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22m%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0d03506bd44db15467257d19f46f1fc1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ItOuR%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue6d50163\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue6d50163\&quot;"> 实矩阵，输出是 </span>
       <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22p%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd4cd21d60552e207f237e82def9029b6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CzRpE%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubb47531e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubb47531e\&quot;"> 维列向量</span></p></td>
    </tr>
   </tbody>
  </table>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6f81fd4f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6f81fd4f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f36c080\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f36c080\&quot;">此外，函数还可直接以矩阵形式 </span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7BF%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb0ee6777e3e06ee35c3b311d33ff8421.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rrJNj%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1b5b3f6c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1b5b3f6c\&quot;"> 存在（即输出为矩阵）——此时可将其视为&quot;实向量函数的高维扩展&quot;（若把向量理解为&quot;单列矩阵&quot;，则矩阵函数是&quot;多列向量的堆叠&quot;）。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud8c0fd89\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud8c0fd89\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;cOSc0\&quot;" id="\&quot;cOSc0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u37658fd7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u37658fd7\&quot;">典型计算场景</span></h4>
  <ol list="\&quot;u59247cae\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;ub48248c6\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u4d6e77f8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4d6e77f8\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2ddbf089\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2ddbf089\&quot;">标量对向量求导</span></strong></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u31dbf1ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u31dbf1ae\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9d0fe210\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9d0fe210\&quot;">数学上，一般定义向量为列向量形式。由于</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%3D%20f(x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20x_n)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F3b6adbe6638db934d55e8201ad4e2759.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22i3m3f%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u05862265\&quot;" id="\&quot;u05862265\&quot;">，所以</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u50e08134\&quot;" id="\&quot;u50e08134\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufce07c10\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufce07c10\&quot;">它对向量变元</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2adf48e1cf80858f0604d2b51eeed4b8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22WFI4b%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc5d91c60\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc5d91c60\&quot;">求导，本质就是对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2adf48e1cf80858f0604d2b51eeed4b8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HVyqB%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ued05b716\&quot;" id="\&quot;ued05b716\&quot;">的每个元素求偏导：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u35ae1c17\&quot;" id="\&quot;u35ae1c17\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_1%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_2%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_n%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ffec6806626b1e828f60e0157c2d55296.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vh6gh%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u474e2a26\&quot;" id="\&quot;u474e2a26\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u51e64deb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u51e64deb\&quot;">例如：<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf1f3c0e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf1f3c0e5\&quot;">函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%3D%20x_1%5E2%20%2B%202x_1x_2%20%2B%20x_2%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F201536d191165231c0d8a0b3f8d84826.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22n5lzD%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0f6d81b0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0f6d81b0\&quot;">，令</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%20%3D%20%5Bx_1%2C%20x_2%5D%5ET%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fabecb11127be2beb57db8560d7c8fd21.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UUGDL%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue5bbf29c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue5bbf29c\&quot;">，则</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u852d32cc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u852d32cc\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%202x_1%20%2B%202x_2%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%202x_1%20%2B%202x_2%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc05157688005d32081b072402f957eb4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22oiczP%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;ue08cd16a\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u9829b27c\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u8e017c2b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8e017c2b\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1bc5f4ba\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1bc5f4ba\&quot;">标量对矩阵求导</span></strong></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2bc518ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2bc518ff\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u54bde673\&quot;" id="\&quot;u54bde673\&quot;">变元</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PWdNZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1b6414e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1b6414e5\&quot;">是一个</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22m%20%5C%5Ctimes%20n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0d03506bd44db15467257d19f46f1fc1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22kNoNc%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3a0c03ae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3a0c03ae\&quot;">的矩阵，可以看成是</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22m%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4760e2f007e23d820825ba241c47ce3b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FPqdc%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u199e93ec\&quot;" id="\&quot;u199e93ec\&quot;">个行向量的组合，每个向量维度为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf378375e7693bdcf9535661c023c02e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FaRi0%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3955f0cd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3955f0cd\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaee1dc76\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaee1dc76\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubb5454af\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubb5454af\&quot;">那么</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F18f3c2855f0e85a1ac2257f64d917144.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KjUOM%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e86af64\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e86af64\&quot;">对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22WsvSP%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3fe32b78\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3fe32b78\&quot;">求导，同样也是对其中的每个元素求导，结果形状与</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zYGSG%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0664227c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0664227c\&quot;">相同：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4aeadc42\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4aeadc42\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20X%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B11%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B12%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B1n%7D%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B21%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B22%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7B2n%7D%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7Bm1%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7Bm2%7D%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_%7Bmn%7D%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fae03038ea1c24e28d032f45757d78362.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22waphB%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u9e030b9c\&quot;" start="\&quot;3\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;uc95e8e45\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u8470e42e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8470e42e\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8ca75e53\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8ca75e53\&quot;">向量对标量求导</span></strong></li>
  </ol>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7bfdf92d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7bfdf92d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc35febc5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc35febc5\&quot;">对于向量函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D(x)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F8d911fa0a1e4604661e2a39e98644b76.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sidiP%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c1c3606\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c1c3606\&quot;">，可以写为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uddf178b3\&quot;" id="\&quot;uddf178b3\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D(x)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20f_1(x)%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20f_2(x)%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20f_m(x)%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2925a5567a991796c6d30555ed66768e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22yI2UH%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u16e2e2be\&quot;" id="\&quot;u16e2e2be\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf0aa666\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf0aa666\&quot;">显然，此时的</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F17ce46d3728e85d6225ef7045b6b2754.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22EMhQs%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uda9c49dc\&quot;" id="\&quot;uda9c49dc\&quot;">可以看作多个函数的组合，对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F712ecf7894348e92d8779c3ee87eeeb0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fWuQl%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u253fa242\&quot;" id="\&quot;u253fa242\&quot;">求导时，只要让其中的每个元素分别对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F712ecf7894348e92d8779c3ee87eeeb0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QWUjv%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2879a36\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2879a36\&quot;">求导即可：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u77cd22aa\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77cd22aa\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7Bd%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%7D%7Bdx%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bdf_1%7D%7Bdx%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bdf_2%7D%7Bdx%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bdf_m%7D%7Bdx%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F9faa9b6057e638767fa88fbc6e1ad5df.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dAuf1%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8cd47a66\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8cd47a66\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f45d8fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f45d8fd\&quot;">例如：<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9c1da3af\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9c1da3af\&quot;">函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D(x)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20x%5E2%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%202x%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%203%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1711e5b100919a1789274d04d9395c66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vJr6T%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u35d1b2b3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u35d1b2b3\&quot;">，则</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u931f7780\&quot;" id="\&quot;u931f7780\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7Bd%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%7D%7Bdx%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%202x%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%202%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdd1ba335be4943f12ed2d538c73d6a77.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OBHAJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <ol list="\&quot;u90ddca05\&quot;" start="\&quot;4\&quot;">
   <li fid="\&quot;u48b391f5\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uc8688fe7\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc8688fe7\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u291af1ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u291af1ac\&quot;">向量对向量求导（了解）</span></strong></li>
