  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u24d28b89\&quot;" id="\&quot;u24d28b89\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0d74cfe2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0d74cfe2\&quot;">类似（3）中的分析，向量函数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fe33506f11c6e145cb7059f97108de32e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MEp6U%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uef42dd85\&quot;" id="\&quot;uef42dd85\&quot;">可以写为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc71da721\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc71da721\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20f_1(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20f_2(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20f_m(%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D)%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F80be4d57fbabf65ef2d9110e2ff7f613.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rQvu0%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u73e667d9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u73e667d9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4395026\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4395026\&quot;">这里</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F17ce46d3728e85d6225ef7045b6b2754.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ifPP5%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7799c08c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7799c08c\&quot;">的每一个元素</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f_i%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbccc235f2749d475b14107feeb0d8c42.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22awWCl%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4aa9187\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4aa9187\&quot;">，都是变元</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2adf48e1cf80858f0604d2b51eeed4b8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GG311%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u692f03d3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u692f03d3\&quot;">为向量的实标量函数。<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucddda3cb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucddda3cb\&quot;">接下来只要应用（1）中的结论，将</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F17ce46d3728e85d6225ef7045b6b2754.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vHVxO%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u592d5a65\&quot;" id="\&quot;u592d5a65\&quot;">中的每个标量函数对</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2adf48e1cf80858f0604d2b51eeed4b8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vzhly%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u457577fd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u457577fd\&quot;">求导即可：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0457f25e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0457f25e\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bf%7D%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20%5C%5Cmathbf%7Bx%7D%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bbmatrix%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_1%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_1%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_1%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_2%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_1%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_n%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_2%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_1%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_2%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_2%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_2%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_n%7D%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cddots%20%26%20%5C%5Cvdots%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_m%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_1%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_m%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_2%7D%20%26%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%26%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20f_m%7D%7B%5C%5Cpartial%20x_n%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bbmatrix%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F18b70a9835413911272a61b3210d0f7f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lqEPA%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
