   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u61503bf5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61503bf5\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2818c138\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2818c138\&quot;">用一个具体例子说明：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c106261\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c106261\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u150bb862\&quot;" id="\&quot;u150bb862\&quot;">假设袋子里有 5 个球（编号 1-5），其中 3 个红球（1, 2, 4），2 个蓝球（3, 5）。</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;u9ae1ce51\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;u7886ce47\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0f3c21c\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0f3c21c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2b1dba6a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2b1dba6a\&quot;">事件 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ff3wC%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9df701e1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9df701e1\&quot;">：「抽到红球」。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u7886ce47\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uba90c926\&quot;" id="\&quot;uba90c926\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9dcae807\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9dcae807\&quot;">事件 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Cm7aX%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5b870544\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5b870544\&quot;">：「抽到的球编号 &gt; 3」。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u7886ce47\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7a29bbd1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7a29bbd1\&quot;">
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd323a7fa4041bfab0129556b389c0e0c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PfMVX%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf398a97f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf398a97f\&quot;">：「抽到编号 &gt; 3 的红球」（只有球 4），所以 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B)%20%3D%201%2F5%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ffadf80982abf5b80eb725ea1e1b3e115.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uXVxp%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u05965bc5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u05965bc5\&quot;">。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u7886ce47\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6777c64\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6777c64\&quot;">
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22EkOsn%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u49087124\&quot;" id="\&quot;u49087124\&quot;">：「抽到编号 &gt; 3 的球」（球 4, 5），所以 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%20%3D%202%2F5%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2635b71fb47c6a1180561359bd79a084.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22EotiG%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u03f0d5a6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u03f0d5a6\&quot;">。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3c30b5d2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3c30b5d2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f51dd04\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f51dd04\&quot;">如果 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1e28bfe42d1264ff2685ba7221b6d855.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lzXwf%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5b218d70\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5b218d70\&quot;"> 直接等于 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fcab37290a351f2a64fecfa9b0d48835d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eet0N%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u33a36e4f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u33a36e4f\&quot;">，那么 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%20%3D%201%2F5%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F197efeb1d169feb61e961bfc043cea60.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rDpZN%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b49624b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b49624b\&quot;">。</span></p>
