    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TWzG0%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue68c3e56\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue68c3e56\&quot;"> 发生），样本空间就缩小到了球 4 和球 5。在这个缩小后的空间中，只有球 4 是红球，所以实际概率应该是 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%221%2F2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F9eb3ee4a5fcee8d1e41f8e10ef10236f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GkuLZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucdfc9bf5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucdfc9bf5\&quot;">。</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u53a40095\&quot;" id="\&quot;u53a40095\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u51cf4c04\&quot;" id="\&quot;u51cf4c04\&quot;">使用公式 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%20%3D%20P(A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B)%20%2F%20P(B)%20%3D%20(1%2F5)%20%2F%20(2%2F5)%20%3D%201%2F2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbbb8959c122660045dfd5d010c8d98c4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HK5nk%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3dc53672\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3dc53672\&quot;">，这与缩小样本空间后的实际概率一致。</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ucdf8c5b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucdf8c5b8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucd5dfeb4\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucd5dfeb4\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uca059e34\&quot;" id="\&quot;uca059e34\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue4d52c84\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue4d52c84\&quot;">总结：为什么要除以 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eg2r8%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9e85528a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9e85528a\&quot;">？</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;u210d2743\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;u430277ff\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u04b9d7bd\&quot;" id="\&quot;u04b9d7bd\&quot;">
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1e28bfe42d1264ff2685ba7221b6d855.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wXBo7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1dd6227e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1dd6227e\&quot;"> 的核心在于「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Hhivk%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubdf0b7a9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubdf0b7a9\&quot;"> 发生后，样本空间缩小到了 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vdgtq%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1f5cb9b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1f5cb9b9\&quot;"> 对应的结果集合」。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u430277ff\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub54e80ce\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub54e80ce\&quot;">
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22StHNE%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u26d2a846\&quot;" id="\&quot;u26d2a846\&quot;"> 衡量了 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22K09B1%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc16a0672\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc16a0672\&quot;"> 在原始样本空间中的「比例」。除以 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XLaEA%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8340f110\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8340f110\&quot;"> 就是把「原始样本空间的度量」缩放到「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VHmFf%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2a50549\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2a50549\&quot;"> 的度量」，从而得到「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dHeym%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uab2d5690\&quot;" id="\&quot;uab2d5690\&quot;"> 发生时 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VXqsd%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufc58bba2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufc58bba2\&quot;"> 的相对比例」。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u430277ff\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u22737581\&quot;" id="\&quot;u22737581\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u047aab08\&quot;" id="\&quot;u047aab08\&quot;">直接使用 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fcab37290a351f2a64fecfa9b0d48835d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22BNMh3%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0f224df3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0f224df3\&quot;"> 忽略了「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22BebYC%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u77dfc9ec\&quot;" id="\&quot;u77dfc9ec\&quot;"> 发生」对样本空间的限制，给出的是「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ch5zm%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u68d640ba\&quot;" id="\&quot;u68d640ba\&quot;"> 和 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YTwth%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7136f52e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7136f52e\&quot;"> 同时发生」的绝对概率，而不是条件概率。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u430277ff\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u60eecaff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u60eecaff\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0c861a01\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0c861a01\&quot;">简单来说：条件概率求的是「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wP42Q%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udb22be5c\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb22be5c\&quot;"> 在 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22icNe7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u379344db\&quot;" id="\&quot;u379344db\&quot;"> 中的比例」，所以要用「</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%20%5C%5Ccap%20B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd323a7fa4041bfab0129556b389c0e0c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wiCG1%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf9936769\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf9936769\&quot;"> 在 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VRU3s%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u383082de\&quot;" id="\&quot;u383082de\&quot;"> 中的比例」，而 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Xms70%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf98e04ce\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf98e04ce\&quot;"> 作为 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qeaUc%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7dc62e6f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7dc62e6f\&quot;"> 在原始空间中的「权重」，实现了这种「比例缩放」。</span></li>
   </ul>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e940a41\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e940a41\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;bzLQh\&quot;" id="\&quot;bzLQh\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0fc790f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0fc790f\&quot;">概率分布</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udb709f57\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb709f57\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8bac5c22\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8bac5c22\&quot;">概率分布，是指用于表述随机变量取值的概率规律。事件的概率表示了一次试验中某一个结果发生的可能性大小。如果试验结果用变量X的取值来表示，则随机试验的概率分布就是随机变量的概率分布，即随机变量的可能取值及取得对应值的概率。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u41af0b9c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41af0b9c\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6d17c898\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6d17c898\&quot;">​</span></strong><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;UduhZ\&quot;" id="\&quot;UduhZ\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4affb743\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4affb743\&quot;">均匀分布</span></strong></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u097c25ef\&quot;" id="\&quot;u097c25ef\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u834fdd96\&quot;" id="\&quot;u834fdd96\&quot;">均匀分布也叫矩形分布，它表示在相同长度间隔的分布概率是等可能的。均匀分布由两个参数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22a%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F26fdbf8e53cb0e48da5f4ddd4aaf5a5c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zbvSb%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc0575dba\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc0575dba\&quot;">和</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22b%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd29c2e5f4926e5b0e9a95305650f6e54.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vZAXZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u53854cd7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u53854cd7\&quot;">定义，它们是数轴上的最小值和最大值，通常缩写为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22U(a%2C%20b)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0104bb08523b433406932ed33ea92dc6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PmTf9%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubbfbb422\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubbfbb422\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf5fa4c6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf5fa4c6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6859ee70\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6859ee70\&quot;">均匀分布的概率密度函数可写为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaee382a8\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaee382a8\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cbegin%7Bcases%7D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bb-a%7D%20%26%20a%20%3C%20x%20%3C%20b%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%200%20%26%20%5C%5Ctext%7B%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%7D%20%5C%5Cend%7Bcases%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd911ded6f9c10272ddb3b1595f769cb6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22z5IaD%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u24d8c477\&quot;" id="\&quot;u24d8c477\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf84ad8e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf84ad8e\&quot;">​</span></strong><br /></p>
  <h5 data-lake-id="\&quot;rUyL9\&quot;" id="\&quot;rUyL9\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6348ac7b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6348ac7b\&quot;">正态分布</span></strong></h5>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2d5f2a34\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2d5f2a34\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u987d97ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u987d97ac\&quot;">正态分布（Normal Distribution）也称高斯分布，是常见的连续概率分布。正态分布在统计学上十分重要，经常用在自然和社会科学来代表一个不明的随机变量。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6eacca3c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6eacca3c\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u596c8f07\&quot;" id="\&quot;u596c8f07\&quot;">若随机变量</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eEDM0%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u18d45992\&quot;" id="\&quot;u18d45992\&quot;">服从一个平均数为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmu%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F756a643380ff53c0692dbc2e7e930a35.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OK0oh%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2beb2cd0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2beb2cd0\&quot;">、标准差为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F788df1ba344b3092def7590d1be6b4d4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TRjlI%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8e2e081a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8e2e081a\&quot;">（方差为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F217d731c58118430ccbb4f9f6d44ce08.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OirdV%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u37431dd6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u37431dd6\&quot;">）的正态分布，则记为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%20%5C%5Csim%20N(%5C%5Cmu%2C%20%5C%5Csigma%5E2)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fcd7004344e6125f5f1e67111895d1e02.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Yqi9G%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u09c67dd1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09c67dd1\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua5f5f05e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua5f5f05e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc2206bea\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc2206bea\&quot;">标准差</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F788df1ba344b3092def7590d1be6b4d4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22x2rMJ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufeab57f5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufeab57f5\&quot;">的计算公式为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u50e59e97\&quot;" id="\&quot;u50e59e97\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%20%3D%20%5C%5Csqrt%7B%5C%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7Bn%7D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20(x_i%20-%20%5C%5Cmu)%5E2%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc89ed6f4ab6a3c3f7ad70638614401ec.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FAt8F%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue567b2ed\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue567b2ed\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf1f7fb95\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf1f7fb95\&quot;">其概率密度函数为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u32748af1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32748af1\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22f(x)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B%5C%5Csigma%5C%5Csqrt%7B2%5C%5Cpi%7D%7D%20e%5E%7B-%5C%5Cfrac%7B(x-%5C%5Cmu)%5E2%7D%7B2%5C%5Csigma%5E2%7D%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F0a2ddac79c15c47f4a923c70914593c4.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zK5z1%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u27a078e0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u27a078e0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u14d8cbcb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u14d8cbcb\&quot;">正态分布的期望</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmu%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F756a643380ff53c0692dbc2e7e930a35.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OpQYW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5bbbaca9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5bbbaca9\&quot;">可解释为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6dc06970\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6dc06970\&quot;">位置参数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucd0d4774\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucd0d4774\&quot;">，决定了分布的位置；其方差</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F217d731c58118430ccbb4f9f6d44ce08.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eSfzx%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucf44bf46\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucf44bf46\&quot;">可解释为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue93a4774\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue93a4774\&quot;">尺度参数</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u72253a3c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u72253a3c\&quot;">，决定了分布的幅度。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf25fe19a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf25fe19a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue1c2ce4b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue1c2ce4b\&quot;">正态分布概率密度函数图：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u85baf670\&quot;" id="\&quot;u85baf670\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;image\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F34523858%2F1766720652761-9aa5dab4-0886-4045-b9cf-1db0c3acdd8d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc717ee88-bf20-4600-a6b9-400d6597ff5%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u91a152d8-9fbb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A556%2C%22height%22%3A354%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A1234052%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A695%2C%22originHeight%22%3A443%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%221.0%20U%2C0%2C020.2%2C%20U%2C0%2CC21.0%200.8%20U%2C0%2C%202-5.0%2C%20U-2%2CC20.5%2C%200.6%20DIO%200.4%200.2%200.0%20-2%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A43%2C%22y%22%3A21%2C%22width%22%3A22%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%221.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A497%2C%22y%22%3A50%2C%22width%22%3A128%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text%22%3A%22U%2C0%2C020.2%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A496%2C%22y%22%3A73%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22U%2C0%2CC21.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A41%2C%22y%22%3A91%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%220.8%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A495%2C%22y%22%3A98%2C%22width%22%3A128%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22U%2C0%2C%202-5.0%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A496%2C%22y%22%3A123%2C%22width%22%3A128%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22U-2%2CC20.5%2C%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A41%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A24%2C%22height%22%3A14%2C%22text%22%3A%220.6%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A13%2C%22y%22%3A203%2C%22width%22%3A24%2C%22height%22%3A43%2C%22text%22%3A%22DIO%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A34%2C%22y%22%3A230%2C%22width%22%3A31%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%220.4%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A299%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%220.2%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A369%2C%22width%22%3A21%2C%22height%22%3A12%2C%22text%22%3A%220.0%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A253%2C%22y%22%3A400%2C%22width%22%3A19%2C%22height%22%3A13%2C%22text%22%3A%22-2%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f4f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua3432937%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1ea8b9e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1ea8b9e9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u98a349f3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u98a349f3\&quot;">正态分布的概率密度函数曲线呈钟形，因此人们又经常称之为钟形曲线。我们通常所说的标准正态分布是位置参数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmu%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fefb02bce4c741fbcc801ec1d8aa2797f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DwAJr%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a1cf29c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a1cf29c\&quot;">，尺度参数</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Csigma%20%3D%201%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb27c7b4693c0110956c6fbf14e38aaf8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22T2DTe%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc90db2f0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc90db2f0\&quot;">的正态分布</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22N(0%2C%201)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F90abd7918c0aa46751fdb38c8a35eb70.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pLv7K%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u69fbd64c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u69fbd64c\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0decaf8a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0decaf8a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua95559c2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua95559c2\&quot;">中心极限定理指出，在特定条件下，一个具有有限均值和方差的随机变量的多个样本的平均值本身就是一个随机变量，其分布随着样本数量的增加而收敛于正态分布。因此，许多与独立过程总和有关的物理量，例如测量误差，通常可被近似为正态分布。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u75122a10\&quot;" id="\&quot;u75122a10\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ube79fde9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube79fde9\&quot;">在numpy中，提供了各种随机函数，可以用来生成服从特定分布的数据。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua83e4819\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua83e4819\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2ba72c70\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2ba72c70\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;LyF4b\&quot;" id="\&quot;LyF4b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u568c31ee\&quot;" id="\&quot;u568c31ee\&quot;">贝叶斯定理</span></h3>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u32782128\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32782128\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b14f9ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b14f9ff\&quot;">贝叶斯定理（Bayes' Theorem）是概率论中的一个核心定理，用于描述在已有条件概率信息的基础上，如何更新或计算事件的概率。它以英国数学家托马斯&middot;贝叶斯的名字命名。贝叶斯定理特别适合处理&quot;逆向概率&quot;问题，即从结果反推原因的概率。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u01385939\&quot;" id="\&quot;u01385939\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6459081e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6459081e\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;MxZch\&quot;" id="\&quot;MxZch\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8fb9fe1c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8fb9fe1c\&quot;">全概率公式</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6ec07dc9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6ec07dc9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u36eec9fb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u36eec9fb\&quot;">对于复杂事件B，它可能有很多种具体情况，发生概率不容易直接求得。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c071501\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c071501\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc012f809\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc012f809\&quot;">这些不同的具体情况可以是一组简单事件，记作A1、A2、…、An，发生的概率P(Ai) 已知；如果它们满足两两</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue4d56ba3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue4d56ba3\&quot;">互不相容</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3158c4d4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3158c4d4\&quot;">、且发生概率之和为 1，就称它们是一个</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e9fbbd1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e9fbbd1\&quot;">完备事件组</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6a44926f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6a44926f\&quot;">。<br /></span><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue046d17e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue046d17e\&quot;">这样，如果知道了在每个简单事件发生的前提下、复杂事件发生的概率（条件概率 P(B| Ai) ），就可以将它们全部合并起来，求出复杂事件的概率了。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uad591e45\&quot;" id="\&quot;uad591e45\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud6349147\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud6349147\&quot;">这个公式就被称为&quot;全概率公式&quot;。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u1b15b93e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1b15b93e\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%20%3D%20P(B%7CA_1)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(A_1)%20%2B%20P(B%7CA_2)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(A_2)%20%2B%20%5C%5Ccdots%20%2B%20P(B%7CA_n)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(A_n)%20%3D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(B%7CA_i)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(A_i)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F695f3bdc85eb4a6acd7099f6555e0b0d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22h316P%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0e017a7f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0e017a7f\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;LzC7m\&quot;" id="\&quot;LzC7m\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0fb6f5b4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0fb6f5b4\&quot;">贝叶斯公式</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0ec9bc2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0ec9bc2\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9498fb98\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9498fb98\&quot;">贝叶斯定理建立在条件概率的基础上，假设有两事件</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Lt3xf%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u32520496\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32520496\&quot;">和</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pgAEB%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b443569\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b443569\&quot;">，贝叶斯定理描述了在</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud4710ca9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud4710ca9\&quot;">已知</span></strong>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XXAHW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9f72062d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9f72062d\&quot;">发生的情况下，</span></strong>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rnIkK%22%7D\&quot;"></card><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3f5fdec9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3f5fdec9\&quot;">发生的概率（通常 B 是果，A 是因）：</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6b6c5fae\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6b6c5fae\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7BP(B%7CA)%20P(A)%7D%7BP(B)%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb753f182d89cfa7b567e343fbd70411f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HVtlr%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u639bf1ed\&quot;" id="\&quot;u639bf1ed\&quot;">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A%7CB)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1e28bfe42d1264ff2685ba7221b6d855.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Spqu7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7fb41eb7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7fb41eb7\&quot;">：后验概率，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fuun7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8c8c20b6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8c8c20b6\&quot;">发生的情况下</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FhxZ3%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0a672308\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0a672308\&quot;">发生的概率。<br /></span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B%7CA)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F064d72782b4c43991f267dbccdf64433.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TcNNi%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u41e8434d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41e8434d\&quot;">：似然概率，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22IIR8L%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf5342cb1\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf5342cb1\&quot;">发生的情况下</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tYmmL%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u317d8182\&quot;" id="\&quot;u317d8182\&quot;">发生的概率。<br /></span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F8a147e409c019f76a61a7b43fb904c4d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DLju9%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u34c1e834\&quot;" id="\&quot;u34c1e834\&quot;">：先验概率，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fde951302f41d4707b9d80ca1af34dd0f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pQqI4%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u606bdef2\&quot;" id="\&quot;u606bdef2\&quot;">发生的概率。<br /></span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZjfSA%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4504b181\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4504b181\&quot;">：</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54f5fb1b07a88521e7b036e3bc7a5e33.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22I3Bi9%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0db3f8a1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0db3f8a1\&quot;">发生的概率，通常通过全概率公式计算。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua9a6ace7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua9a6ace7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4fcda3a4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4fcda3a4\&quot;">在实际问题中通常</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(B)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fca7ad63a270c2ed124d5b722844376ce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YdQzz%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u43066110\&quot;" id="\&quot;u43066110\&quot;">不是直接给出，而是需要通过全概率公式计算。假设样本空间被一组互斥且完备的事件</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22A_1%2C%20A_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20A_n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F3e68a5801f49e87482bf50f6de49253a.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UYQxW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6416f0f\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6416f0f\&quot;">划分，则：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uaabb2c2c\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaabb2c2c\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(A_i%7CB)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7BP(B%7CA_i)%20P(A_i)%7D%7B%5C%5Csum_%7Bj%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(B%7CA_j)%20P(A_j)%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F11024d8ba9ba00df0a3c6c6122ef4857.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xzFYp%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a9d4a9f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a9d4a9f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u755a8ee9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u755a8ee9\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ufed69030\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufed69030\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u052e2fac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u052e2fac\&quot;">例如：某疾病发病率为1%，如果一个人有疾病，检测呈阳性的概率为95%；如果一个人没有疾病，检测呈阳性的概率为5%，现有一人检测结果呈阳性，问他真正患病的概率是多少？</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2d53c173\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2d53c173\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7BP(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D)%20P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D)%7D%7BP(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F80a81d2f7506fe3615b5981fc7da415c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22f8fuy%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u97bb3cfa\&quot;" id="\&quot;u97bb3cfa\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua0b0cf5d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua0b0cf5d\&quot;">首先计算</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fe7fe9cc673d8fe77b7681d02c288d36a.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22RkRNw%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf2d08851\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf2d08851\&quot;">：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u37579192\&quot;" id="\&quot;u37579192\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%20%3D%20P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D)%20%2B%20P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%97%A0%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%7D)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%97%A0%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%7D)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc986492d6512fb3a3b30ed2c3757b5d9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22clvIZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u64085c53\&quot;" id="\&quot;u64085c53\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%3D%200.95%20%5C%5Ctimes%200.01%20%2B%200.05%20%5C%5Ctimes%200.99%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F83f8d032d90d88dcc4de1c22d886eb9b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22M2VRV%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubfa729d9\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubfa729d9\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%3D%200.0095%20%2B%200.0495%20%3D%200.059%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7dd37d36790fa982c691891827c1a290.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tj0Ve%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ufd3fbe5b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufd3fbe5b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2a67a01a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2a67a01a\&quot;">然后计算</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc6a7159355f7df4690fbe59b543ed3fb.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22l4WkT%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udafec107\&quot;" id="\&quot;udafec107\&quot;">：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue90acf06\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue90acf06\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(%5C%5Ctext%7B%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%7D%7C%5C%5Ctext%7B%E9%98%B3%E6%80%A7%7D)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B0.0095%7D%7B0.059%7D%20%5C%5Capprox%200.161%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fad92638c63fd2da03684b9082ceb7aed.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22h4M4E%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u07a726c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u07a726c0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udb9069e3\&quot;" id="\&quot;udb9069e3\&quot;">检测呈阳性的人真正患病的概率为16.1%。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u83c00583\&quot;" id="\&quot;u83c00583\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufe1563cb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufe1563cb\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <h3 data-lake-id="\&quot;E6moV\&quot;" id="\&quot;E6moV\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2061576d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2061576d\&quot;">似然函数</span></h3>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;Y6xHz\&quot;" id="\&quot;Y6xHz\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud468b64a\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud468b64a\&quot;">基本概念</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud7723ccf\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud7723ccf\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8634fb55\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8634fb55\&quot;">概率用于在已知一些参数的情况下，预测接下来在观测上所得到的结果。而似然性则是用于在已知某些观测所得到的结果时，对有关事物之性质的参数进行估值。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u63745542\&quot;" id="\&quot;u63745542\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud2dfafb8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud2dfafb8\&quot;">似然函数是对参数的函数，其定义为在给定参数值的条件下，观察到某个特定数据的概率。换句话说，似然函数是一个关于参数的函数，而不是关于数据的函数。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0a9e5c6\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0a9e5c6\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8e45d3d0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8e45d3d0\&quot;">如果我们有一个参数化的概率模型，其中</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UMXK9%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u53a807b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u53a807b9\&quot;">是观测数据，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22O943Q%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8dd7af3f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8dd7af3f\&quot;">是模型参数，似然函数定义为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udeff4bdd\&quot;" id="\&quot;udeff4bdd\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2f04eddfbff831eb9115b034ee734ae7.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22oGKaW%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2379e7d9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2379e7d9\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub83804eb\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub83804eb\&quot;">这里，</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F07386f3a60ff197be7483a3fe57f5583.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AfoP3%22%7D\&quot;"></card><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue3299721\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue3299721\&quot;">表示在参数为</span></strong>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CtEJn%22%7D\&quot;"></card><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7e0a771b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7e0a771b\&quot;">的情况下，观察到数据</span></strong>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22I3ihG%22%7D\&quot;"></card><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue98cf744\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue98cf744\&quot;">的概率。</span></strong></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u48e59cd1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u48e59cd1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf9893e78\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf9893e78\&quot;">设有一组独立同分布的观测数据</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cmathbf%7BX%7D%20%3D%20(x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cldots%2C%20x_n)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F639f4d1a67c14ab109b89bb293dea860.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CJXnt%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u405fac1a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u405fac1a\&quot;">，并且这些数据服从某个分布（例如正态分布、二项分布等），比如服从参数为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22V3PbR%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5127dcfe\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5127dcfe\&quot;">的某个分布，那么似然函数可以写作：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u42fecc95\&quot;" id="\&quot;u42fecc95\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7C%5C%5Cmathbf%7BX%7D)%20%3D%20P(%5C%5Cmathbf%7BX%7D%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cprod_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F6e9d5871ca2757cfd3bfc36624302787.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MXAZV%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u16987fe1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u16987fe1\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7759b462\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7759b462\&quot;">针对其中存在的乘法，可以使用对数函数将其</span><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud28b9312\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud28b9312\&quot;">转化为加法</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua4c4f8e5\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua4c4f8e5\&quot;">：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u7f1e3f99\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7f1e3f99\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cell(%5C%5Ctheta%7C%5C%5Cmathbf%7BX%7D)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clog%20L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clog%20%5C%5Cleft(%20%5C%5Cprod_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%5C%5Cright)%20%3D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20%5C%5Clog%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fe974ffbb1376e198ecdfca9621691dc5.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pBXNQ%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u0f5f4b36\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0f5f4b36\&quot;" class="\&quot;lake-alert" lake-alert-warning\"="">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u629e681a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u629e681a\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufd30fab8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufd30fab8\&quot;">要理解似然函数及其公式推导，可以从概率与似然的区别、独立同分布的联合概率、对数转换的意义这三个层面逐步拆解：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc5857035\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc5857035\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5d401056\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5d401056\&quot;">一、概率与似然：视角的转换</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u08dd0a97\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08dd0a97\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue999b97b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue999b97b\&quot;">先明确两个核心概念的区别：</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;u7c9e4c34\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;u9b059fb2\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5b6b24d5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5b6b24d5\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4c0cc70\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4c0cc70\&quot;">概率 (Probability)：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3cde429e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3cde429e\&quot;">已知模型的参数（比如抛硬币正面概率 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22p%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd4cd21d60552e207f237e82def9029b6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pKzPk%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u081cdc3e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u081cdc3e\&quot;">），预测&quot;观测数据出现的结果&quot;。公式表示为 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F07386f3a60ff197be7483a3fe57f5583.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22X1HCw%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u80408366\&quot;" id="\&quot;u80408366\&quot;">，其中 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OeXJF%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udf08617a\&quot;" id="\&quot;udf08617a\&quot;"> 是观测数据，</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XezhU%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u00ec2118\&quot;" id="\&quot;u00ec2118\&quot;"> 是模型参数。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u9b059fb2\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u1a9d91e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1a9d91e9\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf67c0cc3\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf67c0cc3\&quot;">似然 (Likelihood)：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5a02e865\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5a02e865\&quot;">已知观测数据的结果（比如抛了3次硬币都是正面），反推&quot;模型参数的可能性&quot;。公式表示为 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc97ade35d482a62cf16361685fb770b9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22q1tuW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaec46262\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaec46262\&quot;">，它本质上是把&quot;概率 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F07386f3a60ff197be7483a3fe57f5583.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Qo4n2%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud8d46afa\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud8d46afa\&quot;">&quot;当作关于参数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Gl6eq%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;udc9bd814\&quot;" id="\&quot;udc9bd814\&quot;"> 的函数，重点关注&quot;参数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HX7V5%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud43dc2d3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud43dc2d3\&quot;"> 如何影响已知数据 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uOq0m%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u760a3cc1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u760a3cc1\&quot;"> 出现的概率&quot;。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u08830219\&quot;" id="\&quot;u08830219\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u61e229ca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61e229ca\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u3dc74141\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3dc74141\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue69741ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue69741ac\&quot;">二、似然函数的定义（以独立同分布为例）</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u68f4b948\&quot;" id="\&quot;u68f4b948\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uaad313b0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uaad313b0\&quot;">假设我们有一组独立同分布 (i.i.d.) 的观测数据 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%20%3D%20(x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cdots%2C%20x_n)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4a28597c4dbe05e24229e3288d1f9ebb.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KLBT7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u599ae41b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u599ae41b\&quot;">，且每个数据都服从由参数 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OYnBE%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua1a1218b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua1a1218b\&quot;"> 决定的概率分布（比如正态分布、二项分布等）。</span></p>
   <ol list="\&quot;uba1623ca\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;uc1088831\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u14e4dbe6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u14e4dbe6\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u966fd250\&quot;" id="\&quot;u966fd250\&quot;">独立事件的联合概率</span></strong></li>
   </ol>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u73bbbe43\&quot;" id="\&quot;u73bbbe43\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u794250bf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u794250bf\&quot;">根据概率论中&quot;独立事件&quot;的性质：若多个事件相互独立，它们的联合概率等于各自概率的乘积。</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u6804311f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6804311f\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud1d01670\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud1d01670\&quot;">对于独立同分布的数据 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cdots%2C%20x_n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fccc3c860b7e9f4f50bd88daccf1ec7ea.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YFFJD%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0efc617b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0efc617b\&quot;">，每个 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22x_i%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F5b13ed0ae41bee9defcf75f2efc5f060.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22italf%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf6eb5fe2\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf6eb5fe2\&quot;"> 出现的概率由参数 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rM1Iy%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ucfef91a2\&quot;" id="\&quot;ucfef91a2\&quot;"> 决定（即 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F119546cc9032b34ece050cbc6ea85d84.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22aHwXR%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u67bb2e54\&quot;" id="\&quot;u67bb2e54\&quot;">）。因此，所有数据同时出现的联合概率为：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uba70b78e\&quot;" id="\&quot;uba70b78e\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20P(x_1%2C%20x_2%2C%20%5C%5Cdots%2C%20x_n%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20P(x_1%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%5C%5Ccdot%20P(x_2%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%5C%5Cdots%20P(x_n%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd9d3d7e8c3089ddd8ae550e799495afb.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22cMp8G%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u4732c6ef\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4732c6ef\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u98a72790\&quot;" id="\&quot;u98a72790\&quot;">用连乘符号简化后：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubed8f7aa\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubed8f7aa\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cprod_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F49d7b714c2b4e70f6870c6923b189c98.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22X6Ggo%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <ol list="\&quot;uc2df53d5\&quot;" start="\&quot;2\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;ufd8cdaa7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u248f6cf4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u248f6cf4\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue2e84b33\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue2e84b33\&quot;">似然函数的引入</span></strong></li>
   </ol>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u87651261\&quot;" id="\&quot;u87651261\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0ab7542e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0ab7542e\&quot;">似然函数 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc97ade35d482a62cf16361685fb770b9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CKygW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2f6c001c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2f6c001c\&quot;"> 的定义是：在&quot;观测到数据 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22S9maA%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u674d3bb3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u674d3bb3\&quot;">&quot;的条件下，参数 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FA10P%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ube1492c7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ube1492c7\&quot;"> 对应的&quot;可能性&quot;。而这种&quot;可能性&quot;恰好可以用&quot;已知 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zOPU4%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub2391277\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub2391277\&quot;"> 时 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22BGS0j%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6b8e4c6e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6b8e4c6e\&quot;"> 出现的概率 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F07386f3a60ff197be7483a3fe57f5583.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GK0NX%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5ae889dc\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5ae889dc\&quot;">&quot;来衡量。因此，似然函数直接定义为：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8273db79\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8273db79\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cprod_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd5f1b02ffa723d35c12946a43193c8b1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KBAHl%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u54980ebb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u54980ebb\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u656ad7e7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u656ad7e7\&quot;">三、对数转换：从&quot;连乘&quot;到&quot;求和&quot;</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ue07be654\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue07be654\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc0dd3457\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc0dd3457\&quot;">似然函数是连乘形式 (</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cprod%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F3a43d8eb928c55797e7106c82357d890.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Og7uw%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uea5bb853\&quot;" id="\&quot;uea5bb853\&quot;">)，但连乘在实际计算中存在两个问题：</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;ue1c00024\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;ueccc52ed\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u940aebfe\&quot;" id="\&quot;u940aebfe\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc76b80f5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc76b80f5\&quot;">数值下溢：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2794e454\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2794e454\&quot;">若数据量 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf378375e7693bdcf9535661c023c02e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22SPWvZ%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5284691b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5284691b\&quot;"> 很大，或多个 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F119546cc9032b34ece050cbc6ea85d84.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22iCUM8%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua00561d1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua00561d1\&quot;"> 是小于1的小数，连乘结果会趋近于0，导致计算误差。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;ueccc52ed\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u4def0a21\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4def0a21\&quot;"><strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc2f944aa\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc2f944aa\&quot;">求导复杂：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf01d31d5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf01d31d5\&quot;">若要对似然函数求最大值（如&quot;最大似然估计&quot;），连乘的导数需用&quot;乘积法则&quot;，计算繁琐。</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0c91cac\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0c91cac\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue80b0181\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue80b0181\&quot;">因此，我们利用对数的性质 (</span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Clog(ab)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clog%20a%20%2B%20%5C%5Clog%20b%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F220b9b7c9f3e3cd1a4b9eba84cb7c4b2.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22f07Zj%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u32d05ed5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u32d05ed5\&quot;">)，将&quot;连乘&quot;转换为&quot;求和&quot;，简化计算：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u0d704b15\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0d704b15\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Clog%20L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20%5C%5Clog%20%5C%5Cleft(%20%5C%5Cprod_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%5C%5Cright)%20%3D%20%5C%5Csum_%7Bi%3D1%7D%5E%7Bn%7D%20%5C%5Clog%20P(x_i%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fea833b090ee2782262ac5e14d80e02d6.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gr8nV%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  </blockquote>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;udd4ece16\&quot;" id="\&quot;udd4ece16\&quot;"><br /></p>
  <h4 data-lake-id="\&quot;e0btN\&quot;" id="\&quot;e0btN\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u679c5d35\&quot;" id="\&quot;u679c5d35\&quot;">极大似然估计</span></h4>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u5eab5824\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5eab5824\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud9d56f6e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud9d56f6e\&quot;">似然函数常用于极大似然估计。我们希望找到使似然函数最大化的参数。这意味着在给定观测数据的情况下，选择最可能生成这些数据的参数值。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u28a3d667\&quot;" id="\&quot;u28a3d667\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u25423782\&quot;" id="\&quot;u25423782\&quot;">​</span><br /></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubcf5f6a3\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubcf5f6a3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2ca42b42\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2ca42b42\&quot;">例如，掷硬币3次，2次正面1次背面，能否依据此结果逆推出正面的概率；正面概率为0.5的概率为多少、正面概率为0.6的概率为多少；最有可能的正面概率是多少？</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uce5b1913\&quot;" id="\&quot;uce5b1913\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud5674fff\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud5674fff\&quot;">我们用</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xu8zd%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u894095b5\&quot;" id="\&quot;u894095b5\&quot;">代表硬币正面朝上的概率，用</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tmP1G%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u35d8b400\&quot;" id="\&quot;u35d8b400\&quot;">代表2次正面1次背面的结果。</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u2e1ae8b4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2e1ae8b4\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9f87090\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9f87090\&quot;">似然函数为：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uf83969de\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf83969de\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20C_3%5E2%20%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F77334459519077ff125275237e8f11ff.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ysT51%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc014c573\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc014c573\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u972ec3ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u972ec3ff\&quot;">当正面概率为0.5时：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uab4db44a\&quot;" id="\&quot;uab4db44a\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.5)%20%3D%20C_3%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%200.5%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(1-0.5)%20%3D%200.375%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb1eb651bcc6e0cc56c1f04d84f095ed8.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Lfoi4%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ub23a54a7\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub23a54a7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufb4bd8b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufb4bd8b8\&quot;">当正面概率为0.6时：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uca728a10\&quot;" id="\&quot;uca728a10\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.6)%20%3D%20C_3%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%200.6%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(1-0.6)%20%3D%200.432%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc0ed881698e04d785246c555d28f5ed3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XJWOL%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uabf3db25\&quot;" id="\&quot;uabf3db25\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u5f5088b9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5f5088b9\&quot;">为了找出极大似然估计，对似然函数取对数并求导，使其等于0：</span></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b1f3cb9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b1f3cb9\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cell(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cln%20L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cln(C_3%5E2%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta))%20%3D%20%5C%5Cln%203%20%2B%202%5C%5Cln%5C%5Ctheta%20%2B%20%5C%5Cln(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdb0d964016ca3c6d1a89d7b13ff1e4c9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Nqpfn%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u17f44161\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17f44161\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7Bd%5C%5Cell(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%7D%7Bd%5C%5Ctheta%7D%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B%5C%5Ctheta%7D%20-%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B1%7D%7B1-%5C%5Ctheta%7D%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F9247967e465c955b9c1440bc36b83f4f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YiRfz%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
  <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u61ade026\&quot;" id="\&quot;u61ade026\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u541db29f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u541db29f\&quot;">解得</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F08106e2d3fe14bd132b6291f4f58fc1b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sVxCg%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9306efca\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9306efca\&quot;">，意味着当掷硬币3次，出现2次正面1次背面的结果时，硬币正面朝上的概率最有可能为</span>
   <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F28955ef49943e21c66dc069fc9a1445f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Aj9qC%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uf7e13c18\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf7e13c18\&quot;">。</span></p>
  <blockquote data-lake-id="\&quot;u040480a6\&quot;" id="\&quot;u040480a6\&quot;" class="\&quot;lake-alert" lake-alert-warning\"="">
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua51b7cfc\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua51b7cfc\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7afbcfa3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7afbcfa3\&quot;">推断「硬币正面朝上的概率 </span>
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22skHm5%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9d0fe5ac\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9d0fe5ac\&quot;">」具体流程步骤如下：</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ua650cde0\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua650cde0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue642ead8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue642ead8\&quot;">(1) 确定概率模型：二项分布</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;ubcdb70b7\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;u32770ebb\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7011d6a3\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7011d6a3\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc50de522\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc50de522\&quot;">每次掷硬币是独立的伯努利试验（只有&quot;正面&quot;或&quot;背面&quot;两种结果），且&quot;正面&quot;的概率固定为 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sCaRy%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u46d9628b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u46d9628b\&quot;">，&quot;背面&quot;概率为 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%221-%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbd12b9436917e98c5e2adf2e237a39e5.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ODF3R%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u14e40aee\&quot;" id="\&quot;u14e40aee\&quot;">。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u32770ebb\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u12bd5c54\&quot;" id="\&quot;u12bd5c54\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u763cdd04\&quot;" id="\&quot;u763cdd04\&quot;">若进行 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf378375e7693bdcf9535661c023c02e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TFbL7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u05fdf222\&quot;" id="\&quot;u05fdf222\&quot;"> 次独立试验，&quot;成功（比如正面）</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22k%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf976ff7fcf17d60490267d18a1e3996.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22P7Njw%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3655c3e9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3655c3e9\&quot;"> 次&quot;的概率服从二项分布，公式为：</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uba3f63c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uba3f63c0\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%20%3D%20k%7Cn%2C%20%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20C_n%5Ek%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Ctheta%5Ek%20%5C%5Ccdot%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%5E%7Bn-k%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa117b99285456e5667d549cb14ec4090.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Oalym%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;u49706b23\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;u34318aba\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u7e0a443e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7e0a443e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4d711b96\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4d711b96\&quot;">其中 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22C_n%5Ek%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7Bn!%7D%7Bk!(n-k)!%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F2d5f9b6bb9ed7240a374a6cec8bdc20f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UP3UW%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u2aaf8b95\&quot;" id="\&quot;u2aaf8b95\&quot;"> 是&quot;从 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22n%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf378375e7693bdcf9535661c023c02e.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wIgnx%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u843342cb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u843342cb\&quot;"> 次中选 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22k%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf976ff7fcf17d60490267d18a1e3996.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VQ31R%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u3d86fed4\&quot;" id="\&quot;u3d86fed4\&quot;"> 次成功&quot;的组合数。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;u34318aba\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u1302e26d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1302e26d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4b7fa7bf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4b7fa7bf\&quot;">在例子中：</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22n%3D3%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F27576ef4ca36a588ac8486a592a09e3f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fZdhH%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud88fe04b\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud88fe04b\&quot;">（掷3次），</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22k%3D2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fbc16f1c31c92cb722d5cb9d7d1e19e12.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hUemY%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u398a3068\&quot;" id="\&quot;u398a3068\&quot;">（2次正面），因此&quot;观测到2正1反&quot;的概率为：</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ubf32b07d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubf32b07d\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22P(X%20%3D%202%7C3%2C%20%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%20C_3%5E2%20%5C%5Ccdot%20%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20%5C%5Ccdot%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%5E%7B3-2%7D%20%3D%203%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F4f0f6d45832e88f0a050b33f494791a3.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22arxtr%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u18d5b9f7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u18d5b9f7\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4a51ae1a\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4a51ae1a\&quot;">(2) 似然函数的定义</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;u9ee4fd4a\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;ubb2d76a0\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ufeb0b037\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufeb0b037\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ue0fcc7dd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue0fcc7dd\&quot;">似然函数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc97ade35d482a62cf16361685fb770b9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22V72eR%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u71a401bf\&quot;" id="\&quot;u71a401bf\&quot;"> 的本质是「给定观测数据 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OgEzx%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u068fec7d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u068fec7d\&quot;"> 时，参数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QdJYe%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u22624cc9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u22624cc9\&quot;"> 对应概率的大小」。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;ubb2d76a0\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u0770d87d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0770d87d\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubc6e0f4f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubc6e0f4f\&quot;">在例子中，观测数据 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22RzQZ1%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1ff83d43\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1ff83d43\&quot;"> 是&quot;2次正面1次背面&quot;，因此似然函数就是上述二项分布的概率（因为我们假设&quot;观测到 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22X%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F94e79ad0c1aabeafef9e2fc4af6adf66.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LE8Dz%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u622895a9\&quot;" id="\&quot;u622895a9\&quot;">&quot;时，参数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fq66r%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud0dc120f\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud0dc120f\&quot;"> 对应的概率就是似然值）：</span></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;uc4dc5670\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc4dc5670\&quot;" style="\&quot;text-align:" center\"="">
    <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%20P(X%7C%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%203%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F9d7eedf2740fa1b02107414d62de144b.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Tw4Co%22%7D\&quot;"></card></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;u634f2f41\&quot;" id="\&quot;u634f2f41\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u0b502060\&quot;" id="\&quot;u0b502060\&quot;">(3) 回答例子中的问题</span></p>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ufadab651\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufadab651\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uec7314a5\&quot;" id="\&quot;uec7314a5\&quot;">&quot;正面概率为0.5的概率为多少、正面概率为0.6的概率为多少？&quot;</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;ub82719ca\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;ucbc03f6f\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u4fd6edde\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4fd6edde\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u7c394ad0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u7c394ad0\&quot;">这里的&quot;概率&quot;其实是「当 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.5%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F99d6f0c5a1c52408489d66a506dc1dce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22k619H%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8830e60c\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8830e60c\&quot;"> 或 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.6%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F21ce2ff2f2bec31e9d8c1a46f540058f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Fh4Y6%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u43c7633b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u43c7633b\&quot;"> 时，观测到&quot;2正1反&quot;的似然值」（即&quot;如果真实 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fed5a4aa5e092e303a69c608582c70db9.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22mT5qF%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u528c80bb\&quot;" id="\&quot;u528c80bb\&quot;"> 是0.5，观测到2正1反的可能性多大？&quot;）。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;ucbc03f6f\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ub42cbf09\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub42cbf09\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u041393b8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u041393b8\&quot;">计算得：</span></li>
   </ul>
   <ul list="\&quot;ub82719ca\&quot;" data-lake-indent="\&quot;1\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;ue02c0476\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uf51086db\&quot;" id="\&quot;uf51086db\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b116e2f\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b116e2f\&quot;">当 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.5%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F99d6f0c5a1c52408489d66a506dc1dce.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sP47s%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufa86dc0d\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufa86dc0d\&quot;"> 时，</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(0.5%7CX)%20%3D%203%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(0.5)%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(1-0.5)%20%3D%200.375%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F15c0a3c054e2db1def6c6803da4a2981.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eWxh9%22%7D\&quot;"></card></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;ue02c0476\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uccba9a19\&quot;" id="\&quot;uccba9a19\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b76870e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b76870e\&quot;">当 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0.6%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F21ce2ff2f2bec31e9d8c1a46f540058f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22iiuby%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ubbc86587\&quot;" id="\&quot;ubbc86587\&quot;"> 时，</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(0.6%7CX)%20%3D%203%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(0.6)%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(1-0.6)%20%3D%200.432%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F1ae19f6f1ef90e7c38acadde856ec938.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Cq1n5%22%7D\&quot;"></card></li>
   </ul>
   <p data-lake-id="\&quot;ud8a1958e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud8a1958e\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u09399e97\&quot;" id="\&quot;u09399e97\&quot;">&quot;最有可能的正面概率是多少？&quot;（即极大似然估计）</span></p>
   <ul list="\&quot;udb5679e5\&quot;">
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u17ce736b\&quot;" id="\&quot;u17ce736b\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u163e7ac1\&quot;" id="\&quot;u163e7ac1\&quot;">我们需要找到 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%20%5C%5Cin%20%5B0%2C1%5D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F06b9147f44b98f4d5b16933cf9ccd21a.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22n3EsF%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc99bf552\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc99bf552\&quot;">，使得似然函数 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta%7CX)%20%3D%203%5C%5Ctheta%5E2(1-%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fdf96f1cc2235d3ccfdeef1dd4720b662.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22aVNoY%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u315b0df8\&quot;" id="\&quot;u315b0df8\&quot;"> 最大。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ua20f15dd\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua20f15dd\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u15e50156\&quot;" id="\&quot;u15e50156\&quot;">方法：对 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta)%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F54cafdab8aa1c35302398b4a0ef1576d.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QNzuX%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;uc6289f34\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc6289f34\&quot;"> 求导，找极值点。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u5e3fd083\&quot;" id="\&quot;u5e3fd083\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u00c620ff\&quot;" id="\&quot;u00c620ff\&quot;">展开 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%203%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20-%203%5C%5Ctheta%5E3%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F7773d2e1cb885c2a052eddf4987eb545.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ltfwR%22%7D\&quot;"></card></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;u66ff3193\&quot;" id="\&quot;u66ff3193\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ud328b8d1\&quot;" id="\&quot;ud328b8d1\&quot;">求导：</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L'(%5C%5Ctheta)%20%3D%206%5C%5Ctheta%20-%209%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F74c69b974c71867c0728970c73ff65e0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22juvqH%22%7D\&quot;"></card></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uca505ab0\&quot;" id="\&quot;uca505ab0\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ub0beba37\&quot;" id="\&quot;ub0beba37\&quot;">令导数为0，解方程 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%226%5C%5Ctheta%20-%209%5C%5Ctheta%5E2%20%3D%200%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F86ba2adfad28dcf1be94aeea6e4d33c0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ABcjR%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u751ea26e\&quot;" id="\&quot;u751ea26e\&quot;">，得 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd35a364377f95b6648905e6247dc8f57.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uZsln%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u4f5dea37\&quot;" id="\&quot;u4f5dea37\&quot;"> 或 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D%20%5C%5Capprox%200.6667%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fb54ace9a138616c71640931b868677e0.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22kWWEI%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u1789195d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u1789195d\&quot;">。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;uc9a7a826\&quot;" id="\&quot;uc9a7a826\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ua767860e\&quot;" id="\&quot;ua767860e\&quot;">验证极大值：当 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fd35a364377f95b6648905e6247dc8f57.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22IZg8N%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u8b2966ab\&quot;" id="\&quot;u8b2966ab\&quot;"> 或 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D1%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F32226a7e59a5ab59e0922e83f33e6908.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zd0G7%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u55efe0c0\&quot;" id="\&quot;u55efe0c0\&quot;"> 时，</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Ctheta)%3D0%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fa54649c2a2b2f936fa7b54b36c57b250.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22NgZGm%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u9433c4e7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u9433c4e7\&quot;">；当 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Ctheta%3D%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Fc7ad8e3eae611dc9661306f97368eee1.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Kph8g%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u41f6861d\&quot;" id="\&quot;u41f6861d\&quot;"> 时，</span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22L(%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D)%20%3D%203%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D)%5E2%20%5C%5Ctimes%20(1-%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D)%20%3D%20%5C%5Cfrac%7B4%7D%7B9%7D%20%5C%5Capprox%200.4444%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2Ffb8b1494d186ff94a3d29f12a902091c.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MTlfP%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u6d8a2435\&quot;" id="\&quot;u6d8a2435\&quot;">，是最大值。</span></li>
    <li fid="\&quot;udf5196e7\&quot;" data-lake-id="\&quot;ue492d4d8\&quot;" id="\&quot;ue492d4d8\&quot;"><span data-lake-id="\&quot;u249c2bf7\&quot;" id="\&quot;u249c2bf7\&quot;">因此，最有可能的正面概率是 </span>
     <card type="\&quot;inline\&quot;" name="\&quot;math\&quot;" value="\&quot;data:%7B%22code%22%3A%22%5C%5Cfrac%7B2%7D%7B3%7D%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F__latex%2F28955ef49943e21c66dc069fc9a1445f.svg%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AWrP8%22%7D\&quot;"></card><span data-lake-id="\&quot;ufefdba89\&quot;" id="\&quot;ufefdba89\&quot;">，这就是极大似然估计的结果。</span></li>
   </ul>
  </blockquote>
